oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Post-Convention Proceedings of the Twenty-Fifth Annual Conference. Opening Session and Events
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Bovine Practitioners, American Association of
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The opening afternoon and evening reception has become a traditional way to begin AABP Annual Conferences. This popular event enables registrants to link up with old friends and form new acquaintances. It is an opportunity also to relax and enjoy an informal meal or browse among the exhibits, become familiar with the Civic Center Arena and to introduce international guests attending the Congress to AABP hospitality and trade exhibits.
